         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Apollonios of the northern ousia and of the Kerkemounis district to Matreas, his most dear friend, greetings. If it seems right to you, send me then for the activities going on here, to cover putlays of [   ], outlays of [     ], for the account of [    ] and of flat house-roofs and of [   ] three hundred drachmas, total 300 drachmas. Year thirty-three of Antoninus Caesar the lord, Mesore 7. (2nd hd.) Give the 300 drachmas."</ab>
         </div>
